QuestData.Title: Grotesque Remains
QuestData.Description:
These grotesque remains are an amalgamation of jelly-like ooze and what appear to be dryad bones.
Guviena Bladesong would be interested in seeing these.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Guviena Bladesong at the Whispering Bluffs.
QuestData.RewardText: These remains... this is horrible! They are turning dryads into mindless piles of ooze!
